Hey Guys this mod a new Craftable BlackSteel Armor To The Game Of Skyrim.

This mod does not conflict with other Armor mods And will not replace the defualt armor in game :) its a Complete Standalone Armor

Stats Are the same as Base Steel armor

TO install use nexus mod manger to Add the File Winrar to ur game and apply the textures and Standalone armor

Enjoy :)
